{"tid":2399656,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被指助還押人士刪電郵及 IG 帳戶　被控妨害司法公正　黃國桐助理等 3 人保釋候訊","createTime":"2021-02-08T10:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T11:24:10.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fe483c37fe66f210abc924fd8bd7a09cb545c7f1","tid":2399656,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"2019 年平安夜，警方在觀塘一間迷你倉內搜出 10 個煙霧彈，18 歲男學生被控兩項管有爆炸品罪。案件今（8 日）在觀塘裁判法院再提堂，<span class=\"red\">男生遭加控一項串謀妨害司法公正罪，指他還押期間，要求兩名探監人士，包括區議員黃國桐的助理，刪除其電郵及 IG 帳號。</span>兩名探監人士亦被控同罪，控方申請兩案合併，押至 3 月 29 日再訊，等候轉介區域法院文件。三名被告獲准保釋，期間不得離港，須向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，首被告鄺**因爆炸品案還押，被指在探監期間，要求被告余**及黃**，刪去其電郵及 IG 等帳戶。<span class=\"red\">懲教署職員聽到相關對話，繼而揭發事件。</span>首被告於去年 2 月 24 日獲准以 20 萬元保釋。"},{"pid":"85b5fbc1a28465f3b7c852d1362ed3a64507324f","tid":2399656,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:16:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E6%B6%89%E5%8A%A9%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E5%88%AA%E9%9B%BB%E9%83%B5%E5%8F%8A-ig-%E5%B8%B3%E6%88%B6-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%A6%A8%E5%AE%B3%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3-%E9%BB%83%E5%9C%8B%E6%A1%90%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86%E7%AD%89-3-%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258A%25A9%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%2588%25AA%25E9%259B%25BB%25E9%2583%25B5%25E5%258F%258A-ig-%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E6%2588%25B6-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25AD%25A3-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25A1%2590%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%25AD%2589-3-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUig6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=66d054cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%2